- I inspected the repository (listed and read relevant files) and updated the ImportJob entity to include the missing fields.
- I added payload and errorMessage fields (with Lombok @Data providing getters/setters) to:
  - src/main/java/com/java_template/application/entity/importjob/version_1/ImportJob.java
