Why this fixes the problem
- ProcessImportProcessor and ValidateImportProcessor expect ImportJob to expose getPayload() and setErrorMessage(String).
- Adding the payload (JsonNode) and errorMessage (String) fields and relying on Lombok-generated accessors resolves the compiler errors referencing those methods.

